title: Star Trek: Enterprise, Season 3/ Series: 1-15
description:
For the past one hundred years have passed since the moment when mankind first broke the light barrier and established the first contact with an alien race . And then came the day when the most advanced starship fleet ship "Enterprise", equipped with the fastest engine "Warp 5" was launched from shipyards and became the first ambassador of humanity in deep space. Under the command of Captain Jonathan Archer, he had to do a lot of scientific discoveries to come into contact with new, unknown civilizations, not just to save the Earth from destruction and ultimately initiate a United Federation of Planets ...
